JavaScript
-
    - JavaScript used to make the HTML as Dynamic.

    - JavaScript is the Scripting Language.

    - JavaScript is the Single Threaded Model.

    - JavaScript Is the Interpreted Language.

1Q.

    Differences Between Programming languages and Intepreted Languages ??


Inclusion Of JavaScript into HTML
-


<script>

    //Business Logic Here

</script>

- we have two types Of Inclusions

1.inline Inclusion / Integreted Inclusion

2.External Inclusion


Ex.

sample.html
-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <script>
         console.log("Welcome to JavaScript !");
    </script>
</html>


Ex.

sample.js
-
alert("Welcome to JavaScript !");


sample.html
-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <script src="sample.js"></script>
</html>



[ Whenevr we run the HTML , AUtomatically Whole HTML Page will be loaded into

  Browser Engine.

  When ever HTML Loaded Successfully , Automatically "document" Object Will Be Prepared By Browser Engine ]



